Class AbstractListItemAccessorImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAccessor, IContainerItemAccessor<Integer>, IPropertyAccessor, Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BranchListItemAccessorImpl, LeafListItemAccessorImpl

    public abstract class AbstractListItemAccessorImpl
extends AbstractContainerItemAccessorImpl<Integer>
    The abstract class AbstractListItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived implementation classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IContainerItemAccessor interface for all List like properties.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
